manifest.name: ioannisxir's Instafel Backup
manifest.author: ioannisxirouxakis
manifest.changelog:
ioannisxirr's Instafel backup v44

-Close friends indicator on the reply sheet of stories made for close friends.
-Now you can share reels sent in chats to your story and to other platforms through the forwarding button next to them.
-Made the grid taller in the profiles.
-You can now create GIF notes (not working in my testing, will work on newer versions).
-Added a Learn more and Watch again screen on the feed video ads so they're not playing again and again.
-Minor changes.
manifest.description: Yeah, most popular backup in the world!
